  "stem": "<p>Line <i>r</i> in the <i>xy</i>-plane has a slope of 7 and passes through the point (0, &minus;2). Which equation defines line <i>r</i>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p><i>y</i> = 7<i>x</i> &minus; 2</p>"
